        "intro_content": "<p>A quality <strong>whetstone</strong> is the single best investment you can make for your <strong>kitchen knives</strong>. Unlike pull-through sharpeners that strip metal unevenly, whetstones give you full control over the edge angle and finish. XinZuo whetstones are manufactured in Yangjiang alongside our knife production, ensuring consistent grit quality and proper hardness for Japanese steel. Whether you need a 1000 grit stone for regular sharpening or a 6000 grit stone for polishing, our whetstone collection has you covered. Most home cooks find a combination 1000/6000 whetstone handles everything from a dull chef knife to fine-tuning a gyuto edge.</p>",
