        "content": "<p>New to <strong>whetstone sharpening</strong>? Our step-by-step guide covers everything from soaking to maintaining the correct angle. <a href=\"/blogs/news/how-to-sharpen-knives-whetstone\">Whetstone sharpening guide</a></p><p>Choosing between 1000, 3000, and 6000 grit? Our <strong>whetstone</strong> grit guide explains which stones you actually need. <a href=\"/blogs/news/whetstone-grit-guide-kitchen-knives\">Whetstone grit guide</a></p><p>Master the difference between 15 and 20 degree sharpening angles for Japanese vs Western kitchen knives. <a href=\"/blogs/news/knife-sharpening-angle-guide\">Sharpening angle guide</a></p><p>Honing steel vs whetstone: understand when to hone and when to sharpen to keep your edge performing. <a href=\"/blogs/news/honing-steel-guide-knife-edge-maintenance\">Honing steel guide</a></p><p>Protect your freshly sharpened edges with our range of knife guards and blade sheaths. <a href=\"/collections/knife-guards\">Shop Knife Guards</a></p><p>The right cutting board protects your knife edge between sharpenings. See our wood and end grain options. <a href=\"/collections/chopping-boards\">Shop Cutting Boards</a></p>",
